StartFrameOffset: Number of frames (in display rate) to skip at the beginning of the sub-sequence.
bCanLoop: Whether this section supports looping the sub-sequence.
EndFrameOffset: Number of frames (in display rate) to skip at the beginning of the sub-sequence.
FirstLoopStartFrameOffset: Number of frames (in display rate) to offset the first loop of the sub-sequence.
HierarchicalBias: Hierachical bias. Higher bias will take precedence.
Flags: Sub-section flags defining how to deal with this sub-sequence
